285
00:15:53,870 --> 00:15:55,360
Do you call yourself a dad?

286
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,550
-Calm down.
-It'll be okay.

287
00:15:56,550 --> 00:15:57,550
-Calm down.
-Don't be anxious.

288
00:15:58,390 --> 00:15:59,870
When we found Chen's phone,

289
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:01,200
the battery had at least half.

290
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,480
I think the pickpocket

291
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:03,550
had already stolen the phone

292
00:16:03,550 --> 00:16:05,390
when you called her at 5:30 PM.

293
00:16:05,790 --> 00:16:07,790
Could it be she noticed her phone was missing,

294
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:08,910
so she went looking for it?

295
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:11,720
It's too risky to steal around Children's Palace.

296
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:13,030
It's not very likely.

297
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:15,390
She must have left Children's Palace

298
00:16:15,510 --> 00:16:17,030
for some reason.

299
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:18,910
But she wouldn't go too far.

300
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:19,720
That way,

301
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:21,270
when she got a call from you,

302
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:23,390
she could return
to Children's Palace's entrance right away.

303
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:25,360
But it's the downtown area.

304
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:27,320
It was also during rush hour.

305
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:29,270
It shouldn't be dangerous.

306
00:16:31,910 --> 00:16:33,750
Except for the small park
in the northwest corner.

307
00:16:35,670 --> 00:16:36,360
She wouldn't do that.

308
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,750
Chen is very timid.

309
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:39,030
She wouldn't dare to sleep alone

310
00:16:39,030 --> 00:16:40,270
