320
00:17:01,550 --> 00:17:03,000
Her teacher reminded me.

321
00:17:03,150 --> 00:17:04,070
Can you show me

322
00:17:04,070 --> 00:17:05,070
how you did it?

323
00:17:05,110 --> 00:17:05,720
Okay.

324
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:09,960
I used this

325
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,480
to connect to this.

326
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:13,070
But it kept prompting failed to connect.

327
00:17:14,670 --> 00:17:16,570
[Warning]

328
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:35,070
Go deeper

329
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:36,160
and search thoroughly!

330
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:37,160
Yes, sir!

331
00:17:44,030 --> 00:17:44,750
Captain Luo!

332
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:46,550
Captain Luo.

333
00:17:47,510 --> 00:17:48,200
What?

334
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:49,590
The teacher helped contact the students

335
00:17:49,590 --> 00:17:50,920
from the surveillance footage.

336
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:52,240
This is their registration information.

337
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:54,550
Based on the kids' recollection,

338
00:17:54,550 --> 00:17:56,200
they went to the public toilet to get changed.

339
00:17:56,310 --> 00:17:58,110
After that, they went to the small park
to snap some photos.

340
00:17:58,400 --> 00:17:59,270
Snap photos?

341
00:17:59,270 --> 00:18:01,000
A student from a photography class
had one assignment to complete.

342
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,480
So he asked several girls to be models.

343
00:18:02,550 --> 00:18:03,160
Several of these kids

344
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:04,750
even brought some clothes for the photo session.

345
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:05,960
It was a while

346
00:18:06,030 --> 00:18:07,640
after they finished taking photos,

347
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:09,110
Zhang Yuchen said
she was going back to Children's Palace.

348
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:10,750
They went separate ways at the park's entrance.

349
00:18:10,750 --> 00:18:11,640
No one knows

350
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:12,640
