351
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:14,000
Here.

352
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:31,000
Hello?

353
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:31,960
I think that the pickpocket

354
00:18:31,960 --> 00:18:33,790
didn't steal the phone from Chen.

355
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:35,480
His excuse was reasonable.

356
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:37,030
I think she left her phone

357
00:18:37,030 --> 00:18:37,790
during the photo shoot.

358
00:18:38,030 --> 00:18:38,920
How did you know?

359
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:40,550
Mr. Zhang tried to turn on

360
00:18:40,550 --> 00:18:41,920
the child's phone remotely around six o'clock

361
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:42,880
but failed.

362
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:44,880
He didn't make any mistakes
while operating the application.

363
00:18:45,110 --> 00:18:46,110
So I deduce

364
00:18:46,720 --> 00:18:48,160
someone took out the battery

365
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:49,680
from the child's phone at the time.

366
00:18:52,070 --> 00:18:54,920
The thief picked up the phone at 6:30 PM.

367
00:18:55,790 --> 00:18:57,110
They didn't have to put it back

368
00:18:57,310 --> 00:18:58,880
after taking the battery out.

369
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:00,240
And they might not know

370
00:19:00,240 --> 00:19:01,510
what kind of applications

371
00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:02,680
are installed on the phone.

372
00:19:04,830 --> 00:19:07,310
So I came up with the greatest possibility.

373
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:17,750
Hurry!

374
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:18,440
Leave our things here.

375
00:19:20,590 --> 00:19:21,270
Let's go.

376
00:19:22,750 --> 00:19:24,310
Time to take some photos!

377
00:19:24,310 --> 00:19:25,350
Come here quickly.

378
00:19:43,550 --> 00:19:45,240
Someone took advantage of Chen's time

379
00:19:46,030 --> 00:19:47,880
while she changed her clothes
or posed for photos

380
00:19:48,480 --> 00:19:49,880
