386
00:20:03,310 --> 00:20:04,110
(At this time,)

387
00:20:04,750 --> 00:20:05,720
(someone suggested)

388
00:20:06,590 --> 00:20:07,830
(finding it at the small park.)

389
00:20:11,350 --> 00:20:12,310
It's you.

390
00:20:12,310 --> 00:20:12,920
Let's go.

391
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:14,830
(And they volunteered to go with her.)

392
00:20:15,550 --> 00:20:17,270
(She must have trusted this person.)

393
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,200
(Someone her age.)

394
00:20:20,270 --> 00:20:21,240
(A kid.)

395
00:21:16,740 --> 00:21:17,330
Captain Luo.

396
00:21:17,740 --> 00:21:18,660
When the teacher from Children's Palace

397
00:21:18,660 --> 00:21:19,530
called the students,

398
00:21:19,530 --> 00:21:20,740
was there any call

399
00:21:20,740 --> 00:21:22,020
