400
00:21:22,770 --> 00:21:23,940
Tell me! Stop daydreaming.

401
00:21:23,940 --> 00:21:24,530
Okay.

402
00:21:24,570 --> 00:21:25,900
Which one was not answered by the parents?

403
00:21:25,900 --> 00:21:26,770
I think there was one.

404
00:21:28,180 --> 00:21:28,810
It's her.

405
00:21:28,940 --> 00:21:29,610
Her name is Su...

406
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:33,420
Su Ruowan?

407
00:21:33,420 --> 00:21:36,870
[Emergency Contact: Su Lingnai, Mother]

408
00:21:38,330 --> 00:21:39,770
She's Su Lingnai's daughter.

409
00:21:39,770 --> 00:21:40,740
She just came of age.

410
00:22:37,020 --> 00:22:39,330
Hello, is there anyone home?

411
00:22:46,570 --> 00:22:48,050
Is there anyone home?

412
00:22:48,180 --> 00:22:50,260
I'm a tenant who just moved upstairs.

413
00:22:50,810 --> 00:22:51,850
Sorry,

414
00:22:51,850 --> 00:22:53,570
but my place was leaking.

415
00:22:53,570 --> 00:22:54,660
Did it leak into your place?

416
00:23:24,700 --> 00:23:25,290
Move aside!

417
00:24:36,770 --> 00:24:37,420
Sir!

418
00:24:38,290 --> 00:24:39,740
This is Qu Tong's dress.

419
00:24:43,770 --> 00:24:44,700
She just left.

420
00:24:45,570 --> 00:24:47,130
She didn't have time to close the music box.

421
00:24:47,940 --> 00:24:49,290
Where could she be now?

422
00:25:50,530 --> 00:25:52,660
He doesn't care about me anymore!

423
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:43,130
When Chen noticed her phone had gone missing,

424
00:26:43,660 --> 00:26:45,260
the first thing she'd do was find a phone

425
00:26:45,260 --> 00:26:46,420
to text her dad.

426
00:26:46,610 --> 00:26:48,090
It was very likely that Su Ruowan used

427
00:26:48,090 --> 00:26:49,900
the excuse of going to her home to make a call home

428
00:26:50,130 --> 00:26:52,050
to lure Chen to leave with her.

429
00:26:52,290 --> 00:26:53,850
Without any transport,

430
00:26:53,980 --> 00:26:55,260
Chen wouldn't want to go too far.

431
00:26:56,220 --> 00:26:57,570
The place Su Ruowan chose

432
00:26:57,570 --> 00:26:58,850
[XWI Children's Palace]
wouldn't be far from Children's Palace.

433
00:26:59,420 --> 00:27:00,090
One kilometer.

434
00:27:00,420 --> 00:27:01,050
No,

435
00:27:02,020 --> 00:27:02,740
five hundred meters.

436
00:27:15,460 --> 00:27:16,460
What was Su Lingnai's registered address

437
00:27:16,900 --> 00:27:18,770
20 years ago?

438
00:27:19,420 --> 00:27:20,050
Wait.

439
00:27:24,740 --> 00:27:26,020
What is it, Wu?

440
00:27:26,460 --> 00:27:27,090
Captain Luo,

441
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:28,220
we installed a bug

442
00:27:28,220 --> 00:27:29,130
in Xu Dongyu's room.

443
00:27:29,330 --> 00:27:31,020
There were two incoming calls.

444
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:31,940
He heard them.

445
00:27:31,940 --> 00:27:32,700
But he didn't answer.

446
00:27:32,980 --> 00:27:34,370
Is it possible that he knew he was being watched?

447
00:27:34,370 --> 00:27:35,180
Captain Luo, over here.

448
00:27:35,180 --> 00:27:36,900
We've traced the number that called.

449
00:27:36,900 --> 00:27:38,290
[No. 56, Luojie Road, Xindong District]
The landline address is at...

450
00:27:38,290 --> 00:27:40,420
No. 56, Luojie Road.

451
00:27:40,900 --> 00:27:42,290
Sir, how did you know?

452
00:27:42,290 --> 00:27:43,090
Bring Pei Su with you.

453
00:27:43,090 --> 00:27:44,570
We're taking Su Ruowan in. He would come in handy.

454
00:27:44,570 --> 00:27:45,180
Move!

455
00:27:48,260 --> 00:27:50,380
He doesn't care about me anymore!

456
00:27:50,940 --> 00:27:53,940
He doesn't care about me anymore.

457
00:27:56,500 --> 00:27:57,330
Open the door!

458
00:27:57,900 --> 00:27:59,460
