459
00:27:59,460 --> 00:28:00,570
I'm trying to sleep here!

460
00:28:02,570 --> 00:28:03,700
What's going on inside?

461
00:28:03,700 --> 00:28:04,700
Open the door! Open up!

462
00:28:05,610 --> 00:28:06,770
If you don't, I'll call the police.

463
00:28:07,330 --> 00:28:09,180
Why are you watching a horror movie

464
00:28:09,220 --> 00:28:10,370
