are the only ones living here?

466
00:28:15,810 --> 00:28:17,700
I'm sorry, mister.

467
00:28:18,180 --> 00:28:19,610
My parents aren't home.

468
00:28:20,090 --> 00:28:22,050
I can't open the door for any stranger.

469
00:28:22,770 --> 00:28:24,090
I'll keep quiet.

470
00:28:24,530 --> 00:28:25,290
What?

471
00:28:25,810 --> 00:28:26,740
A kid?

472
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:28,050
Come out!

473
00:28:28,180 --> 00:28:29,770
I'll help your parents to teach you a lesson.

474
00:28:31,460 --> 00:28:33,090
Come out now!

475
00:28:33,980 --> 00:28:34,980
Mister,

476
00:28:35,700 --> 00:28:36,700
I'm sorry.

477
00:28:36,940 --> 00:28:38,370
Can't I just apologize?

478
00:28:38,370 --> 00:28:39,810
What did you say? I can't hear you.

479
00:28:39,980 --> 00:28:40,850
You were loud

480
00:28:40,850 --> 00:28:42,090
when screaming just now.

481
00:28:42,740 --> 00:28:43,420
Open this door!

482
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:44,900
Quickly!

483
00:29:10,050 --> 00:29:10,660
Freeze!

484
00:29:43,610 --> 00:29:44,460
Su Ruowan.

485
00:29:49,370 --> 00:29:50,090
It's okay.

486
00:29:58,740 --> 00:29:59,810
Where's the criminal you want to catch?

487
00:30:08,850 --> 00:30:10,220
Why is there another kid here?

488
00:30:14,770 --> 00:30:16,570
Where's the kidnapper who was with you?

489
00:30:25,610 --> 00:30:26,810
Unbelievable.

490
00:30:28,500 --> 00:30:30,020
He forced a kid to be his decoy

491
00:30:30,020 --> 00:30:31,500
while he was hiding out.

492
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:33,850
It's the first time

493
00:30:34,530 --> 00:30:35,900
I've encountered such a sneaky criminal.

494
00:30:35,900 --> 00:30:36,810
Am I right, Captain Luo?

495
00:30:41,770 --> 00:30:42,850
Have you caught the bad guy?

496
00:30:47,050 --> 00:30:47,770
Yes.

497
00:30:50,260 --> 00:30:51,020
Little girl,

498
00:30:52,020 --> 00:30:52,900
it's okay.

499
00:30:53,980 --> 00:30:55,420
I've already subdued the bad guy.

500
00:30:56,610 --> 00:30:58,460
This place is surrounded by SID.

501
00:30:58,530 --> 00:30:59,530
He won't be able to escape.

502
00:31:00,330 --> 00:31:01,530
We'll protect you.

503
00:31:02,260 --> 00:31:04,020
