504
00:31:05,130 --> 00:31:05,900
Isn't it heavy?

505
00:31:07,700 --> 00:31:08,330
It's okay.

506
00:31:09,740 --> 00:31:11,050
We're here to help you.

507
00:31:12,330 --> 00:31:13,980
Did anyone kidnap you

508
00:31:15,260 --> 00:31:16,370
or coerce you?

509
00:31:32,500 --> 00:31:34,090
Give the knife to me.

510
00:31:34,530 --> 00:31:36,660
After that, show us who the bad guy is.

511
00:31:36,660 --> 00:31:37,290
Is that okay?

512
00:31:39,700 --> 00:31:41,050
Was it Xu Dongyu?

513
00:31:41,850 --> 00:31:43,260
He used you

514
00:31:43,700 --> 00:31:44,940
to kidnap Qu Tong.

515
00:31:46,570 --> 00:31:47,610
Did he do anything

516
00:31:49,420 --> 00:31:50,900
to hurt you?

517
00:31:57,260 --> 00:31:57,980
Don't be afraid.

518
00:31:58,130 --> 00:31:59,050
It's all over.

519
00:31:59,530 --> 00:32:00,530
I know

520
00:32:00,900 --> 00:32:02,420
you're a good girl.

521
00:32:04,290 --> 00:32:05,330
It was the bad guy

522
00:32:05,330 --> 00:32:07,130
