-Are you okay, baby?

529
00:33:14,050 --> 00:33:14,940
Are you injured?

530
00:33:14,940 --> 00:33:16,090
Does your arm hurt?

531
00:33:16,090 --> 00:33:17,180
What happened to your hand?

532
00:33:18,330 --> 00:33:19,090
Don't be scared.

533
00:33:21,050 --> 00:33:22,290
There, there. I'm here.

534
00:33:22,530 --> 00:33:23,500
I'm here.

535
00:33:23,850 --> 00:33:24,660
Don't be scared.

536
00:33:24,740 --> 00:33:25,290
Doctor!

537
00:33:25,290 --> 00:33:25,850
Her arm.

538
00:33:25,850 --> 00:33:27,500
-Please check on her.
-How did this happen?

539
00:33:27,810 --> 00:33:28,700
-You're okay now.
-What is going on?

540
00:33:28,700 --> 00:33:29,290
Let's go.

541
00:33:29,290 --> 00:33:29,940
Captain Luo,

542
00:33:30,020 --> 00:33:31,740
