543
00:33:31,740 --> 00:33:32,330
Yes.

544
00:33:32,330 --> 00:33:32,980
Inform Wu.

545
00:33:32,980 --> 00:33:33,570
Yes, sir.

546
00:33:36,570 --> 00:33:37,530
How's Chen?

547
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:39,180
Except for being scared

548
00:33:39,180 --> 00:33:39,980
