when you work overtime?

570
00:34:54,570 --> 00:34:56,980
Usually, we'll have a sumptuous feast
at the roadside stall.

571
00:34:56,980 --> 00:34:58,300
Some exquisite

572
00:34:58,530 --> 00:34:59,500
and high-end ones,

573
00:34:59,500 --> 00:35:00,340
like hamburgers.

574
00:35:04,460 --> 00:35:05,940
I'm not someone hard to support, like you.

575
00:35:05,940 --> 00:35:07,170
Do you think I can afford to spend?

576
00:35:08,940 --> 00:35:10,050
There's a hotel ahead

577
00:35:10,050 --> 00:35:11,730
that serves a nice buffet.

578
00:35:12,250 --> 00:35:13,860
One-night stay costs half of my monthly salary.

579
00:35:13,860 --> 00:35:14,730
I can send you there.

580
00:35:14,860 --> 00:35:16,860
The incense in their hotel lobby suffocates me.

581
00:35:16,860 --> 00:35:18,210
And they don't have a tub in their room.

582
00:35:18,380 --> 00:35:19,050
I won't get used to it.

583
00:35:19,500 --> 00:35:20,530
Excuse me, Mr. Pei.

584
00:35:20,530 --> 00:35:22,050
You usually play or fool around.

585
00:35:22,050 --> 00:35:23,300
You're also fussy.

586
00:35:23,300 --> 00:35:24,380
Without working,

587
00:35:24,570 --> 00:35:25,340
does your family have enough money

588
00:35:25,340 --> 00:35:26,860
for you to spend your whole life?

589
00:35:28,730 --> 00:35:30,420
How do you know I'm not working?

590
00:35:30,420 --> 00:35:31,650
What kind of work would you do?

591
00:35:31,780 --> 00:35:32,690
Do you have a salary?

592
00:35:32,690 --> 00:35:33,940
What about social insurance?

593
00:35:34,170 --> 00:35:35,300
We don't need social insurance and salaries

594
00:35:35,300 --> 00:35:37,170
because we usually receive stock dividends.

595
00:35:38,340 --> 00:35:38,980
All right.

596
00:35:39,730 --> 00:35:41,570
I won't stand in the way of your efforts

597
00:35:41,780 --> 00:35:42,820
to work hard for Xinzhou.

598
00:35:44,020 --> 00:35:44,780
I'll get going now.

599
00:37:11,650 --> 00:37:13,900
[Du Jia]

600
00:37:22,170 --> 00:37:22,940
Mr. Pei,

601
00:37:23,380 --> 00:37:24,130
are you okay?

602
00:37:26,770 --> 00:37:28,250
It's only a minor injury.

603
00:37:28,900 --> 00:37:29,770
What did you find out?

604
00:37:31,980 --> 00:37:33,090
I've checked the surveillance footage.

605
00:37:33,210 --> 00:37:34,340
The registration number was rented.

606
00:37:34,570 --> 00:37:35,940
The vehicle's owner is clean too.

607
00:37:36,570 --> 00:37:37,290
It looks

608
00:37:37,290 --> 00:37:39,090
[Cause of accident: Traffic light failure]
like a normal accident

609
00:37:39,090 --> 00:37:40,860
[It happened 1.5 km from Chenguang Junction.]
because the traffic light malfunctioned.

610
00:37:44,350 --> 00:37:47,250
[The car from the right
takes the main responsibility.]

611
00:37:55,380 --> 00:37:56,860
Just like your dad's accident.

612
00:37:59,860 --> 00:38:01,130
It looks like

613
00:38:01,460 --> 00:38:02,940
they did it really early this time.

614
00:38:13,570 --> 00:38:14,290
Du Jia,

615
00:38:15,820 --> 00:38:17,730
they rejected the plan for the 13th District.

616
00:38:18,860 --> 00:38:20,290
It was just as you expected.

617
00:38:21,290 --> 00:38:22,460
The 13th District

618
00:38:22,610 --> 00:38:24,250
is very important to them, as expected.

619
00:38:25,540 --> 00:38:26,460
That's not enough.

620
00:38:27,290 --> 00:38:28,770
I still don't know the secret in that piece of land

621
00:38:28,770 --> 00:38:29,820
in the 13th District.

622
00:38:30,730 --> 00:38:32,090
Did you find anything on Sunshine Fund?

623
00:38:32,650 --> 00:38:33,730
I need more time.

624
00:38:34,340 --> 00:38:36,380
The names on the surface

625
00:38:36,380 --> 00:38:37,420
are insignificant.

626
00:38:37,820 --> 00:38:39,210
The people behind the fund are overseas.

627
00:38:39,380 --> 00:38:40,290
It's complicated.

628
00:38:40,730 --> 00:38:41,650
I need to dig deeper.

629
00:38:46,420 --> 00:38:48,690
If only I could remember more.

630
00:38:53,980 --> 00:38:54,860
Stop

631
00:38:55,570 --> 00:38:57,210
pushing yourself too hard.

632
00:38:58,500 --> 00:38:59,770
You've waited for so many years.

633
00:39:08,340 --> 00:39:08,980
So?

634
00:39:09,460 --> 00:39:10,570
Should I send you back home?

635
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:28,920
[Fairfield by Marriott]

636
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:31,900
[Special Investigation Department]

637
00:39:31,900 --> 00:39:33,770
We took Xu Dongyu in.
He's now in the interrogation room.

638
00:39:33,770 --> 00:39:35,090
Su Ruowan is in another room.

639
00:39:35,090 --> 00:39:36,090
Qiao is keeping watch.

640
00:39:36,340 --> 00:39:37,060
Are you planning...

641
00:39:37,060 --> 00:39:38,690
Has the blood on Qu Tong's clothes been tested?

642
00:39:38,690 --> 00:39:40,290
Yes, it's hers.

643
00:39:40,460 --> 00:39:41,170
But

644
00:39:41,380 --> 00:39:42,730
according to the medical examiner,

645
00:39:42,820 --> 00:39:43,770
it was a massive loss of blood.

646
00:39:43,860 --> 00:39:45,540
The likelihood of being alive is basically...

647
00:39:48,170 --> 00:39:48,860
Mr. Guo?

648
00:39:50,820 --> 00:39:52,060
So this is Guo Feiling's...

649
00:39:58,250 --> 00:39:58,980
Mr. Guo.

650
00:39:58,980 --> 00:39:59,730
Officer.

651
00:39:59,730 --> 00:40:00,460
Why are you...

652
00:40:01,500 --> 00:40:03,130
Did you come looking for me this afternoon

653
00:40:03,290 --> 00:40:04,690
because you were going to re-investigate

654
00:40:04,690 --> 00:40:06,060
that case?

655
00:40:07,460 --> 00:40:08,340
My daughter

656
00:40:08,540 --> 00:40:10,420
hasn't been found for so many years.

657
00:40:12,090 --> 00:40:12,980
I heard

658
00:40:13,090 --> 00:40:14,610
you just found a girl

659
00:40:15,060 --> 00:40:15,940
alive.

660
00:40:15,980 --> 00:40:16,900
Is that true?

661
00:40:19,060 --> 00:40:20,250
Have you caught the suspect?

662
00:40:27,020 --> 00:40:28,060
Is there

663
00:40:28,420 --> 00:40:30,170
a hope of finding out about Ling's case too?

664
00:40:30,540 --> 00:40:31,500
And that man...

665
00:40:31,610 --> 00:40:32,210
Is he

666
00:40:32,500 --> 00:40:34,170
Wu Guangchang's accomplice?

667
00:40:42,730 --> 00:40:43,570
Mr. Guo,

668
00:40:44,340 --> 00:40:46,170
we're still investigating this case.

669
00:40:46,570 --> 00:40:48,290
There are some details we can't disclose.

670
00:40:48,900 --> 00:40:50,130
But trust us.

671
00:40:50,540 --> 00:40:51,730
We'll do our best

672
00:40:51,940 --> 00:40:52,610
to give you

673
00:40:52,940 --> 00:40:54,900
and the families of other victims an answer.

674
00:41:03,250 --> 00:41:04,420
You should go home and get some rest.

675
00:41:12,520 --> 00:41:17,400
[Special Investigation Department]

676
00:41:17,450 --> 00:41:20,900
[Justice will never lose its glory in darkness]

677
00:41:20,900 --> 00:41:22,060
I did not.

678
00:41:23,340 --> 00:41:24,540
I'll say this one last time.

679
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:26,900
I didn't kidnap any girls

680
00:41:26,900 --> 00:41:28,380
or kill anyone.

681
00:41:28,500 --> 00:41:30,210
You've watched the recording from the dashcam.

682
00:41:30,210 --> 00:41:31,690
You followed me, bugged me,

683
00:41:31,690 --> 00:41:33,570
and did a genetic screening on me.

684
00:41:33,770 --> 00:41:34,690
I just want to know.

685
00:41:35,650 --> 00:41:36,650
In Xinzhou,

686
00:41:36,650 --> 00:41:38,380
you've violated a person's basic human rights

687
00:41:38,380 --> 00:41:39,650
to such an extent.

688
00:41:40,060 --> 00:41:41,650
Does this meet the founding purpose

689
00:41:41,650 --> 00:41:42,820
of the Special Investigation Department

690
00:41:42,820 --> 00:41:43,860
to safeguard the rights
and interests of every citizen?

691
00:41:46,460 --> 00:41:48,060
If you have objections

692
00:41:48,060 --> 00:41:49,090
to the Special Investigation Department's
handling procedures,

693
00:41:49,090 --> 00:41:50,770
you can file a complaint
with the Ministry of Supervision.

694
00:41:50,770 --> 00:41:52,290
We will explain in detail
the compliance and legality

695
00:41:52,290 --> 00:41:54,250
of this case-handling procedure.

696
00:41:54,250 --> 00:41:56,420
This is the basic right you have in Xinzhou.

697
00:41:56,500 --> 00:41:57,650
But before that,

698
00:41:57,650 --> 00:41:58,420
Mr. Xu,

699
00:41:58,540 --> 00:42:00,090
please fulfill your civic obligations

700
00:42:00,090 --> 00:42:01,290
and accept our interrogation first.

701
00:42:08,170 --> 00:42:08,820
Okay.

702
00:42:09,820 --> 00:42:10,460
Go ahead.

703
00:42:11,060 --> 00:42:12,570
Su Ruowan took her female classmate

704
00:42:12,570 --> 00:42:14,170
and unlawfully detained the victim.

705
00:42:14,170 --> 00:42:15,820
During that time, she called you twice.

706
00:42:15,820 --> 00:42:17,060
In front of everyone, she identified you

707
00:42:17,060 --> 00:42:18,820
as the one who instructed her to do it.

708
00:42:18,820 --> 00:42:19,610
Mr. Xu,

709
00:42:19,940 --> 00:42:20,730
how do you explain this?

710
00:42:20,730 --> 00:42:21,540
Excuse me for a bit.

711
00:42:21,900 --> 00:42:22,820
Do those from the SID

712
00:42:22,820 --> 00:42:24,130
handle cases without evidence?

713
00:42:24,900 --> 00:42:25,500
Yes, I admit.

714
00:42:26,340 --> 00:42:27,540
I know that girl.

715
00:42:29,770 --> 00:42:30,690
So what?

716
00:42:31,340 --> 00:42:32,290
Are you making me a criminal

717
00:42:32,690 --> 00:42:33,730
based on a phone call

718
00:42:34,770 --> 00:42:35,690
and a child's word?

719
00:42:39,500 --> 00:42:40,980
I finally understand

720
00:42:41,500 --> 00:42:43,500
what trumped-up charges mean.

721
00:42:47,020 --> 00:42:48,770
Why did Su Ruowan call you?

722
00:42:49,250 --> 00:42:50,500
And why did she accuse you?

723
00:42:56,060 --> 00:42:56,820
Have they compared

724
00:42:56,820 --> 00:42:58,380
the shoe size of the suspect
to the shoe prints found

725
00:42:58,380 --> 00:42:59,210
at the scene of Qu Tong's disappearance?

726
00:42:59,380 --> 00:43:00,090
Hanyang is currently
conducting the comparison.

727
00:43:00,090 --> 00:43:02,380
Her mom and I are in a relationship.

728
00:43:05,250 --> 00:43:06,650
I didn't reveal it this afternoon

729
00:43:07,500 --> 00:43:09,250
because I didn't want to get myself into trouble.

730
00:43:11,420 --> 00:43:13,130
I was the one who took care of her mom's funeral.

731
00:43:15,650 --> 00:43:17,060
I've had a crush on Su Lingnai since childhood.

732
00:43:18,210 --> 00:43:19,170
But she didn't like me.

733
00:43:20,540 --> 00:43:22,460
She rather lived a miserable life

734
00:43:23,340 --> 00:43:24,650
than be with me.

735
00:43:26,340 --> 00:43:27,730
It was when she realized

736
00:43:27,730 --> 00:43:29,130
that she was going to die

737
00:43:31,570 --> 00:43:32,820
only did she selfishly decide

738
00:43:34,060 --> 00:43:35,540
to give me a little bit of warmth.

739
00:43:39,820 --> 00:43:40,820
It even moved me

740
00:43:41,570 --> 00:43:42,570
to tears.

741
00:43:44,020 --> 00:43:45,730
I even wanted to marry her.

742
00:43:47,820 --> 00:43:48,570
If she had managed

743
00:43:48,570 --> 00:43:49,900
to hold out until this day,

744
00:43:51,130 --> 00:43:53,420
I would have been Su Ruowan's stepfather.

745
00:44:00,340 --> 00:44:02,170
It's because I'm not her legal guardian

746
00:44:02,170 --> 00:44:04,500
that it's difficult for me to adopt her.

747
00:44:06,090 --> 00:44:07,420
I could only take my time to figure things out.

748
00:44:08,570 --> 00:44:10,940
I met her material needs.

749
00:44:11,610 --> 00:44:12,690
So it's normal

750
00:44:12,690 --> 00:44:13,610
for her to call me

751
00:44:13,610 --> 00:44:14,900
if she needs anything.

752
00:44:14,900 --> 00:44:15,900
But you didn't answer her call.

753
00:44:16,210 --> 00:44:17,610
Yes, I didn't answer

754
00:44:17,770 --> 00:44:19,460
because I knew I was bugged.

755
00:44:19,460 --> 00:44:20,500
Why should I answer her call?

756
00:44:20,500 --> 00:44:21,730
Even if it weren't her who made that call,

757
00:44:21,730 --> 00:44:23,730
like calls from the courier or food delivery,

758
00:44:24,130 --> 00:44:25,090
I wouldn't have answered either.

759
00:44:28,090 --> 00:44:29,900
I do have the right
to retain the last bit of freedom

760
00:44:29,900 --> 00:44:31,460
under the pressure of public authority, right?

761
00:44:32,570 --> 00:44:33,650
So are you saying

762
00:44:34,090 --> 00:44:35,540
that Su Ruowan is framing you?

763
00:44:35,540 --> 00:44:36,460
Sir,

764
00:44:37,820 --> 00:44:39,130
I don't know

765
00:44:39,130 --> 00:44:41,820
how much Su Ruowan is involved in this matter.

766
00:44:41,820 --> 00:44:43,860
And I don't know why she said that.

767
00:44:44,210 --> 00:44:45,210
But if she did it,

768
00:44:45,210 --> 00:44:46,570
I would feel sad.

769
00:44:47,290 --> 00:44:49,170
Her mom had ignored her since she was young.

770
00:44:50,980 --> 00:44:52,570
But if I were to compare,

771
00:44:53,860 --> 00:44:55,820
I can say I'm a responsible stepfather.

772
00:44:57,380 --> 00:44:58,650
She grew up without guidance and supervision.

773
00:44:59,730 --> 00:45:01,610
She would have
inappropriate behaviors sometimes.

774
00:45:02,250 --> 00:45:03,500
And I scolded her.

775
00:45:04,690 --> 00:45:06,130
Perhaps she's a little rebellious

776
00:45:07,170 --> 00:45:07,980
toward me.

777
00:45:11,210 --> 00:45:12,980
Perhaps she doesn't even know what she's saying.

778
00:45:14,020 --> 00:45:15,130
Someone might have enticed her into doing it.

779
00:45:19,250 --> 00:45:20,860
It's okay. No matter what the reason is,

780
00:45:22,500 --> 00:45:23,570
I won't blame her.

781
00:45:24,820 --> 00:45:26,090
I hope you can

782
00:45:26,460 --> 00:45:27,610
investigate this matter properly

783
00:45:28,170 --> 00:45:29,020
and prove it with evidence.

784
00:45:29,020 --> 00:45:30,250
Don't give me that righteous speech.

785
00:45:30,730 --> 00:45:31,900
You've been hiring part-time cleaners

786
00:45:31,900 --> 00:45:33,900
to clean the Sus' old residence

787
00:45:34,090 --> 00:45:35,900
and have been paying the utility bills
from your account.

788
00:45:36,060 --> 00:45:38,060
[User Inquiry Form]
Why are you maintaining an unoccupied house?

789
00:45:38,130 --> 00:45:39,900
You clearly have something to hide.

790
00:45:54,210 --> 00:45:54,980
Sir,

791
00:45:56,340 --> 00:45:57,690
does maintaining an old house

792
00:45:58,420 --> 00:45:59,820
have to have something to do

793
00:45:59,820 --> 00:46:01,540
with the kidnapping and murder?

794
00:46:02,900 --> 00:46:04,290
If I understand you correctly, you're saying

795
00:46:04,290 --> 00:46:05,940
that the municipal administration
should also be responsible

796
00:46:05,940 --> 00:46:07,460
for all the cases occurring in Xinzhou, right?

797
00:46:10,210 --> 00:46:10,940
Do what I say.

798
00:46:11,170 --> 00:46:11,820
Ask him

799
00:46:12,210 --> 00:46:13,500
where he was on the night of the 27th.

800
00:46:13,650 --> 00:46:14,770
Where were you

801
00:46:14,980 --> 00:46:15,820
on the 27th at night?

802
00:46:15,820 --> 00:46:16,610
I was reading at home.

803
00:46:16,610 --> 00:46:17,500
Who can prove that?

804
00:46:17,500 --> 00:46:18,940
I am a freelancer.

805
00:46:19,340 --> 00:46:20,610
It's common to stay home and read.

806
00:46:20,610 --> 00:46:22,250
Why did you rent a car
when you were reading at home?

807
00:46:22,250 --> 00:46:23,610
Sir, what do you mean?

808
00:46:23,610 --> 00:46:24,860
On the evening of the 27th,

809
00:46:24,860 --> 00:46:25,940
you drove and tailed

810
00:46:25,940 --> 00:46:27,250
a school bus from Xiling.

811
00:46:27,250 --> 00:46:28,130
You waited for an opportunity

812
00:46:28,130 --> 00:46:30,060
to make a move on one of the 11 girls on the bus.

813
00:46:30,060 --> 00:46:30,730
But

814
00:46:30,730 --> 00:46:32,820
you happened to witness
the kidnappers hijacking the school bus.

815
00:46:33,090 --> 00:46:34,290
During the process,

816
00:46:34,460 --> 00:46:35,570
a girl named Qu Tong

817
00:46:35,570 --> 00:46:36,730
escaped from the bus.

818
00:46:37,170 --> 00:46:38,460
She ran into you and Su Ruowan.

819
00:46:38,940 --> 00:46:39,770
Out of trust,

820
00:46:39,940 --> 00:46:41,020
she asked for your help

821
00:46:41,020 --> 00:46:42,170
and got into your car.

822
00:46:42,290 --> 00:46:43,540
She never thought she would end up

823
00:46:43,540 --> 00:46:44,940
being ruined by a bastard like you.

824
00:46:44,940 --> 00:46:45,860
This is so...

825
00:46:45,860 --> 00:46:46,820
Where's Qu Tong?

826
00:46:52,540 --> 00:46:53,650
I never met her.

827
00:46:54,130 --> 00:46:55,340
I don't even know her.

828
00:46:55,340 --> 00:46:56,860
Your license plate number was captured
by the surveillance camera on the road

829
00:46:56,860 --> 00:46:58,060
where the bus had passed.

830
00:46:58,130 --> 00:46:59,460
What else do you have to say about that?

831
00:47:03,820 --> 00:47:05,060
Well, I have a question.

832
00:47:05,900 --> 00:47:07,900
What time was it on the night of the 27th?

833
00:47:07,900 --> 00:47:09,020
Don't you know?

834
00:47:09,610 --> 00:47:10,980
I really don't know.

835
00:47:20,610 --> 00:47:21,340
Fine.

836
00:47:21,730 --> 00:47:23,500
Since you guys want to trick me on purpose,

837
00:47:24,250 --> 00:47:25,210
I'm sure you won't tell me

838
00:47:25,210 --> 00:47:26,250
the exact time.

839
00:47:28,170 --> 00:47:30,090
But can I say something to defend myself?

840
00:47:32,460 --> 00:47:33,690
If the case happened

841
00:47:33,690 --> 00:47:35,340
before midnight on the 27th,

842
00:47:35,340 --> 00:47:37,060
I'm afraid I wouldn't be able to make it there.

843
00:47:37,460 --> 00:47:38,900
You know where I live.

844
00:47:39,380 --> 00:47:40,420
From my house

845
00:47:40,690 --> 00:47:42,130
to the location you mentioned in Xiling

846
00:47:42,130 --> 00:47:43,770
would take at least three hours by car.

847
00:47:44,540 --> 00:47:45,860
That's before we take the weather

848
00:47:45,860 --> 00:47:47,090
